hat you want is step 2 (and 3, 4, 5 &amp; 6), and actually good content for at least ten more articles. So you should subscribe, through RSS, or the newsletter, right now! ( And yes, that is the action I want you to take, so do it, now! )</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://yoast.com/blog-seo-secret/\">Dirty little secret of Blog SEO</a> is a post from <a href=\"http://yoast.com/about-me/\">Joost de Valk</a>&#39;s <a href=\"http://yoast.com\">Yoast - Tweaking Websites</a>. \n\nA good WordPress blog needs good hosting, you don\'t want your blog to be slow, or, even worse, down, do you? Check out my thoughts on <a href=\"http://yoast.com/wordpress-hosting/\">WordPress hosting</a>!</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/joostdevalk/~4/vDl47m7jmEU\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";}i:9;a:14:{s:5:\"title\";s:39:\"The complete guide to duplicate content\";s:4:\"link\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/joostdevalk/~3/ciojzhSgNdQ/\";s:4:\"guid\";s:24:\"http://yoast.com/?p=3635\";s:8:\"comments\";s:135:\"http://yoast.com/complete-guide-duplicate-content/#utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=complete-guide-duplicate-content#comments\";s:3:\"wfw\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentrss\";s:131:\"http://yoast.com/complete-guide-duplicate-content/#utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=complete-guide-duplicate-contentfeed/\";}s:5:\"slash\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";s:2:\"27\";}s:7:\"pubdate\";s:31:\"Thu, 09 Dec 2010 15:41:56 +0000\";s:2:\"dc\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";s:13:\"Joost de Valk\";}s:8:\"category\";s:3:\"SEO\";s:11:\"description\";s:751:\"<p>In doing my work as an SEO, I constantly encounter people who do not \"get\" the concept of duplicate content. It\'s as old as the search engines themselves, and SEO\'s have been fixing it since day one, but we apparently still need to do more about it. That\'s why I decided to take some time [...]</p><p><a href=\"http://yoast.com/complete-guide-duplicate-content/\">The complete guide to duplicate content</a> is a post from <a href=\"http://yoast.co