>\n<p><a href=\"http://yoast.com/slideshare-oembed/\">SlideShare plugin, now with oEmbed</a> is a post from <a href=\"http://yoast.com/about-me/\">Joost de Valk</a>&#39;s <a href=\"http://yoast.com\">Yoast - Tweaking Websites</a>. \n\nA good WordPress blog needs good hosting, you don\'t want your blog to be slow, or, even worse, down, do you? Check out my thoughts on <a href=\"http://yoast.com/wordpress-hosting/\">WordPress hosting</a>!</p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/joostdevalk/~4/fuHtqORcF9Y\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:96:\"http://yoast.com/slideshare-oembed/#utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=slideshare-oembed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"\n			\n			\n			\n			\n			\n			\n			\n			\n			\n			\n			\n			\n			\n			\n			\n			\n			\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:25:\"Presentations from SAScon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/joostdevalk/~3/795Wj3fYuus/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"http://yoast.com/?p=4225\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:121:\"http://yoast.com/presentations-from-sascon/#utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=pres