 can, the time to listen to this album for the first (good) time, to get it at its absolute best, is to wait until you’ve lost faith in almost everything. At the very least wait until you reach a point when you’re looking for clarity of some kind, for although you won’t find any here, it should be a moving experience while you look.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">At its peak, this album is a big dash of cream in a large black, bitter coffee of a day. A strangely uncomfortable, deflating-then-uplifting smack in the gob of a cd that will leave you worse than you felt when you started, and surely leave you wondering why on earth you ever put it on in the first pace. But my God, do put it on.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">The whole thing drips of October and Halloween and cool Fall air and lunchtime Anthropology seminars and the clocks going back.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Demolition','','inherit','closed','closed','','270-revision-6','','','2010-12-03 20:10:13','2010-12-03 20:10:13','',270,'http://waterstreetgm.org/2010/12/03/270-revision-6/',0,'revision','',0),(313,1,'2010-12-04 00:36:21','2010-12-04 00:36:21','<div id=\"_mcePaste\">\r\n<div id=\"_mcePaste\">\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><a rel=\"attachment wp-att-311\" href=\"http://waterstreetgm.org/2010/12/03/demolition/album-ryan-adams-demolition/\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-311\" title=\"album-Ryan-Adams-Demolition\" src=\"http://waterstreetgm.org/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/album-Ryan-Adams-Demolition-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" /></a>If I had just three words, they’d all be: DEMOLITION. It’s most certainly an avenue you need need need to go down. But march forward not in haste! This is not an album you put on while having a glass of wine, warming up the barbeque and waiting for the onions to go translucent in the frying pan on Saturday evening.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">If you could choose, and surely you can, the time to listen to this album for the first (good) time, to get it at its abso