re for your photos, launch a blog first. A blog is easy to build, will force you to think about content, design and branding, and will get the marketing ball rolling. Next, add a gallery feature to display your photos, and maybe after that add the online ordering.\r\n\r\nYou’re best off to start with tiny little pieces that you can launch quickly.  Get some momentum rolling and you’ll be able to feel confident that you’re actually getting something done, rather that just work on a huge, never ending project.','Launch, launch, launch','','inherit','closed','closed','','930-revision-2','','','2011-01-05 22:43:52','2011-01-06 02:13:52','',930,'http://waterstreetgm.org/2011/01/05/930-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(933,1,'2010-05-06 22:45:19','2010-05-07 02:15:19','I took some pictures a few nights ago for <a href=\"http://matthewbyrne.net \">Matthew Byrne</a>. He is releasing his first CD, <em>Ballads</em>, in a couple of weeks. Here\'s some results:<img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-938\" title=\"Matthew Byrne-2\" src=\"http://waterstreetgm.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/Matthew-Byrne-2-450x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"350\" /><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-939\" title=\"Matthew Byrne-1\" src=\"http://waterstreetgm.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/Matthew-Byrne-1-450x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"350\" /><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-941\" title=\"Matthew Byrne\" src=\"http://waterstreetgm.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/Matthew-Byrne-450x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" /><a rel=\"attachment wp-att-940\" href=\"http://waterstreetgm.org/2010/05/06/marvelously-matthew/matthew-byrne-by-jud-haynes/\"><img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-940\" title=\"Matthew Byrne by Jud Haynes\" src=\"http://waterstreetgm.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/Matthew-Byrne-by-Jud-Haynes-323x500.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" /></a>','Marvelously Matthew','','publish','closed','closed','','marvelously-matthew','','','2011-01-06 16: