ong: it was idealistic, and overflowing with neat tools and great notions.\n\nStewart and his team put out several issues of The Whole Earth Catalog, and then when it had run its course, they put out a final issue. It was the mid-1970s, and I was your age. On the back cover of their final issue was a photograph of an early morning country road, the kind you might find yourself hitchhiking on if you were so adventurous. Beneath it were the words: \"Stay Hungry. Stay Foolish.\" It was their farewell message as they signed off. Stay Hungry. Stay Foolish. And I have always wished that for myself. And now, as you graduate to begin anew, I wish that for you.\n\nStay Hungry. Stay Foolish.\n\nThank you all very much.','Steve Jobs','','inherit','closed','closed','','1030-revision','','','2011-01-06 21:44:16','2011-01-07 01:14:16','',1030,'http://waterstreetgm.org/2011/01/06/1030-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(1158,1,'2011-01-15 09:24:44','2011-01-15 12:54:44','[browsershot url=\"http://www.neveinspired.com/\" width=\"350px\"]','Neve Inspired','','publish','closed','closed','','neve-inspired','','','2011-06-04 17:30:13','2011-06-04 21:00:13','',0,'http://waterstreetgm.org/?p=1158',0,'post','',0),(1782,1,'2011-06-04 17:30:34','2011-06-04 21:00:34','<img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-1256\" title=\"fontsinusecom-full\" src=\"http://waterstreetgm.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/fontsinusecom-full-500x479.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"350\" />','Fonts in Use','','inherit','closed','closed','','1255-autosave','','','2011-06-04 17:30:34','2011-06-04 21:00:34','',1255,'http://waterstreetgm.org/2011/06/04/1255-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(1033,1,'2011-01-06 17:04:14','2011-01-06 20:34:14','I\'ve been admiring the work of <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">UUUUU</span> on his jQuery module <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Masonry</span> for a while and always wanted to try it out with Wordpress. Turns out that it isn\'t too difficult at all.','Using jQuery Mason