sion-16','','','2011-01-26 17:04:14','2011-01-26 20:34:14','',1218,'http://waterstreetgm.org/2011/01/26/1218-revision-16/',0,'revision','',0),(1235,1,'2011-01-26 23:00:26','2011-01-27 02:30:26','Winter has finally come. Victoria Park looks like this. The haze in the middle of the first and last shots is my breath—it was -9°C.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-1236\" title=\"_MG_5234\" src=\"http://waterstreetgm.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/MG_5234-500x333.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-1239\" title=\"_MG_5333\" src=\"http://waterstreetgm.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/MG_5333-500x333.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-1238\" title=\"_MG_5330\" src=\"http://waterstreetgm.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/MG_5330-500x333.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" />\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft size-medium wp-image-1237\" title=\"_MG_5326\" src=\"http://waterstreetgm.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/MG_5326-500x500.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" />','Victoria Park','','publish','closed','closed','','victoria-park','','','2011-01-26 23:29:11','2011-01-27 02:59:11','',0,'http://waterstreetgm.org/?p=1235',0,'post','',0),(1236,1,'2011-01-26 22:58:19','2011-01-27 02:28:19','','_MG_5234','','inherit','closed','closed','','_mg_5234','','','2011-01-26 22:58:19','2011-01-27 02:28:19','',1235,'http://waterstreetgm.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/MG_5234.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1237,1,'2011-01-26 22:58:25','2011-01-27 02:28:25','','_MG_5326','','inherit','closed','closed','','_mg_5326','','','2011-01-26 22:58:25','2011-01-27 02:28:25','',1235,'http://waterstreetgm.org/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/MG_5326.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1238,1,'2011-01-26 22:58:30','2011-01-27 02:28:30','','_MG_5330','','inherit','closed','closed','','_mg_5330','','','2011-01-26 22:58:30','2011-01-27 02:28:30','',1235,'http:/