step is counting the money as it rolls in.','The case for single-page websites','','inherit','closed','closed','','1636-revision-21','','','2011-05-05 08:56:09','2011-05-05 12:26:09','',1636,'http://waterstreetgm.org/2011/05/05/1636-revision-21/',0,'revision','',0),(1665,1,'2011-05-05 12:14:04','2011-05-05 15:44:04','Well, you can file the <a href=\"http://uncrate.com/stuff/bosch-ixo-vino/\">Bosch Cork Screw Drill</a> under <em>Why didn\'t I think of that. </em>','Bosch Cork Screw Drill','','publish','closed','closed','','bosch-cork-screw-drill','','','2011-05-05 12:14:04','2011-05-05 15:44:04','',0,'http://waterstreetgm.org/?p=1665',0,'post','',0),(1666,1,'2011-05-05 12:14:04','2011-05-05 15:44:04','','Bosch Cork Screw Drill','','inherit','closed','closed','','1665-revision','','','2011-05-05 12:14:04','2011-05-05 15:44:04','',1665,'http://waterstreetgm.org/2011/05/05/1665-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(1667,1,'2011-05-06 08:38:15','2011-05-06 12:08:15','<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xP1-oquwoL8\">Four golden minutes</a> of Nicholas Cage <em>completely </em>losing it.','Nicholas Cage loses his shit','','publish','closed','closed','','nicholas-cage-loses-his-shit','','','2011-05-06 08:38:15','2011-05-06 12:08:15','',0,'http://waterstreetgm.org/?p=1667',0,'post','',0),(1668,1,'2011-05-06 08:38:15','2011-05-06 12:08:15','','Nicholas Cage loses his shit','','inherit','closed','closed','','1667-revision','','','2011-05-06 08:38:15','2011-05-06 12:08:15','',1667,'http://waterstreetgm.org/2011/05/06/1667-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(1669,1,'2011-05-06 10:36:41','2011-05-06 14:06:41','So <a href=\"http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/asia-pacific/a-photo-tour-inside-and-around-bin-ladens-compound/article2010516/?from=2012407\">this</a> is what a mansion in Pakistan might look like.','Bin Laden\'s Mansion','','publish','closed','closed','','bin-ladens-mansion','','','2011-05-06 10:36:41','2011-05-06 14:06:41','',0,'http://waterstreetgm.org/?p=1669',0,'post